data.text:
@jasquinn99 Hi, once you have reported your bag you can check the status of your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU
In this link you will also find a contact tab which has a phone number and a message box to keep in touch with the airport that is handling your bag.

Kind regards, Rebecka

@RommyLiinda Hi, since you are unable to make the payment on our website, I suggest you to call our support. 
Please find your regional phone number here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards, Rebecka

@Hihaj Hej! Det går dessvärre inte att ångra avbokningen, om man är osäker på hur man går till väga för att omboka sin biljett på hemsidan är det viktigt att man ringer oss för hjälp med ombokningen.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@djulius Hello, if you are certain that the password meet these requirements I would recommend that you contact us on live-chat or phone so we can help you investigate a bit more https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@stephman97 Hello, the check-in on the airport will open about 2 hours before your planned departure.

Best regards,
Anton.

@djfgiugno Hello, please contact our live-chat or phone support with your Eurobonus questions and they will help you from here https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@MTuittila Hello! At this moment we have no more information indicating that flights will be added to/from this destination before March 2022 unfortunately.

Best regards,
Anton.

@Skaubo Hej, tack för er feedback. Om ni inte har möjlighet att ringa oss så går det bra att kontakta oss via FB Messenger eller Live-chat https://t.co/cIkJt9kPnF för hjälp med att lägga till husdjur på resan.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@youdamannowdogg Hello! Please contact us on Messenger or Live-chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj with your booking details so we can help you take a look at this.

Best regards,
Anton.

@thohus Hej! Vi har dessvärre inte möjlighet att kolla på enskilda bokningar över Twitter men jag rekommenderar att du kontaktar oss via Messenger eller Live-chat https://t.co/cIkJt9kPnF så kan vi undersöka vilka ombokningsregler era biljetter hade.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@Andersson_123 Hej! 

Ett munskydd skyddar både dig och andra i planet, och det kravet kommer nog vara kvar så länge Covid-19 är ett problem. Man behöver munskydd på alla våra flyg även på långresor, men man kan fortfarande ta av den en kort stund medans man äter.

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@Chris_Trivedi Hi! 

We should be open, i can't see the document you sent but if you call us and wait a bit then you will get in queue, you can also contact our live chat if you want help. https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

//Best regards, Dennis.

@ohmyldn_ Hello!
We have several different types of tickets with different departure and rebooking rules so that there will be an alternative for everyone and on the payment side, Europ Assistance offers travel insurance.

Kind regards, Anja!

@Andersson_123 Hej! 
Om du lider av en sjukdom som hindrar dig från att bära ansiktsmask som täcker näsa och mun ska du visa läkarintyg som beskriver anledningen. Du behöver också ett intyg på ett negativt SARS Cov-2 test (PCR eller antigen) som är max 48 timmar gammalt. 

Hälsningar, Anja!

@Andersson_123 Hej! 
Vi med internationella myndigheter och tillsynsmyndigheter. En av dessa är Europeiska unionens byrå för luftfartssäkerhet, EASA. SAS har valt att följa EASA:s rekommendationer och en av dessa är rådet att bära ansiktsmask när du reser.

Hälsningar, Anja!

@c_hennes Hello!
If you receive an error message or the page does not respond, you will have to bring the travel documents to the airport for inspection. 
Kind regards, Anja!

@thohus Hej!
De allra flesta av SAS biljetter kan inte nedgradeas till en lägre bokningslass. Vid eventuell ombokning ombokas kunden till samma bokningklass du som kund tidigare bokat,  allternativt en högre bokningsklass, då tillkommer eventuell mellanskillnad. 

Hälsningar, Anja!

@peterhanke Hi, you will need to follow the Danish travel restrictions in order to enter the country. Please find information here: https://t.co/YhT9mVc7De
SAS has no additional rules apart from everyone from age 6 and above need to wear a facemask while traveling.

Kind regards, Rebecka

@andJuliet99 Hi, you can make a claim for unexpected expenses with our Customer Care department. You can make your claim here: https://t.co/OzrIxYNv63
Make sure to save any receipts and add them to your claim so that we can assist you in the best possible way.
Kind regards, Rebecka

@iluvwendysworld Hi Wendy
When you fly with SAS hand luggage is always included. Right now it is limited to 1 item per person and nothing more than that https://t.co/2UUXPRN2w1
Kind regards /Anna

@C4R3Bear Hi
Contact us on Facebook messenger , live chat or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj with bookingreference and we can help you further.
Kind regards /Anna

@Filosophation Hi Filosophation
Please contact us on Facebook messenger , live chat or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj and we can help you further.
Kind regards /Anna

@zachary83284988 Hi zachary
I advice you to check with the local authority's of what rules apply regarding animals and passport.
Kind regards /Anna

@alanliv71828247 Hi Alan 
Please contact us on Facebook messenger , live chat or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj and we can look at your refund , advice booking reference.
Kind regards /Anna

@SjefKirurgen Hej Bjørn
Det är svårt att svara på hur stor påverkan det kommer bli då vi inte har så mycket information just nu men vi försöker såklart lösa det på bästa sätt om vi blir påverkad och kunderna blir kontaktad via SMS eller e-post
Hälsningar /Anna

@FrankOxley Hi Frank
We do not have any direct flights for that route at the moment, if it will be reinstated it will be able to book via https://t.co/saQXo2wpQa so keep yourself updated by the webpage.
Kind regards /Anna

@woocon Unfortunately we are not able to assist with specific cases or bookings here over Twitter, please contact our live-chat support for help with your double-charge.

With best regards,
Anton.

@HiljavanKampen Hello, the information on our website is up to date. The carry-on allowance restriction applies on our Domestic, within Scandinavia, to/from European flights in SAS Go and SAS Plus as well as Intercontinental flights in SAS Go. 

Best regards,
Anton.

@woocon Hi. I'm sorry to hear that you got double charged, in these cases however the first payment is usually returned to you automatically within 3-5 business days but I recommend that you contact our live-chat so they can take a look at this https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

//
Anton.

@kristiannissen Okej jag förstår, då rekommenderar jag att du kontaktar vår support så kan de försöka hjälpa dig att felsöka problemet med inloggningen https://t.co/RDEH7uxbwJ

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@alfadelta Hello, the drone batteries must be carried in your carry-on baggage and they need to be individually protected to prevent short-circuits.

With best regards,
Anton.

@zoidberg99 Hi. I am sorry to hear that your flight was rescheduled. To apply for a refund please contact us by live-chat or phone with your booking details. Contact information can be found at https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@melia_mickey Hello. I'm sorry to hear that you missed the connection and I hope this was solved at the airport. If not you can locate our phone numbers at https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@kristiannissen Hej, har du provat med både WiFi och 4G/5G anslutning för att se om det gör någon skillnad? Vänligen kolla även om du har någon VPN eller liknande aktiverad på ditt nätverk som kan orsaka problem.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@SjefKirurgen Hej! De kunder som eventuellt kommer att påverkas av strejken kommer att kontaktas via email/sms.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@andreakqp We apologize if you have still not received your refund, however we are not able to assist you here via social media. Please contact our phone or chat support with your booking details for assistance.

Best regards,
Anton.

@amatistagrrl Hi Melissa 
Contact us on face book messenger , live chat or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj and we can assist.
Kind regards /Anna

@_Blench_ HI T.
You can not bring something additional to hand luggage right now , it is limited to 1 item per person https://t.co/2UUXPRN2w1
Kind regards /Anna

@lukedurett Hello Luke 
You are welcome to contact our customer service via Facebook messenger or live chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj and we will assist you with your questions.
Kind regards /Anna

@EilifEriksen Hi Eilif
Please contact our customer service by Facebook messenger , live chat or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj with your bookings and we will assist you further.
Kind regards/Anna

@Krebthekreb Hej Kreb
För tillfället är den inte det. Du finner informationen via denna länk https://t.co/uHgETi2pF7 gå nästan längst ned till "changes to our services" så uppdateras det där.
Hälsningar /Anna

@mightymarten Hej Mårten
Gitarr packar du i ett hard case och den går som ett vanligt bagage alltså inte special. https://t.co/1vERZG2roy Vill boka biljett där du kan ta med gitarren in i kabin och ha ett säte till den behöver du ringa oss och boka det.
Vänliga hälsningar /Anna

@Rocketpants_ Hi Robbie
It is hard to say, please contact us on Facebook messenger or live chat with your booking reference and we can look at your handling time. https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards /Anna

@nkindler Hello Noah 
If you still have problems please contact us on Face book messenger , live char or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj and we will assist.
Kind regards /Anna

@ivanconinx Hello Ivan 
I can not find any cancelled flight in ours system , please contact us by Facebook messenger , live chat or phone so we can have a look at this and advice your bookingreference https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards /Anna

@LizT1 @LizT1 We don't have access to that baggage system. It's handled by the arrival service at the airport where you landed. I would advice you to contact them. You can find more information here https://t.co/KQdOdrH9TM
We apologize for any inconvenience.
Best regards, Mikael.

@ALWAYSALESSON Hi! 

Okay if you can't find your booking reference then i recommend that you contact our customer service by phone so they can help you find it and add your eurobonus number to the booking. You can find our contact info here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

//Best regards, Dennis.

@Katharina_EJ Hi, I am sorry to hear that your bag has been delayed, please make sure you have set up a delayed report in order to ensure we retrieve it for you as soon as possible: https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3
Once set up you can track your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU
Kind regards, Rebecka

@articainaBF Hi, I am sorry to hear that your bag got delayed. If you haven't made a report on the airport when you landed, you can create one here: https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 
If you already have a report you can track it here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU
Kind regards, Rebecka

@SaltLiberation Hi, in order to have a look at what options you have available for your booking, you will need to contact our support by phone: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
We are currently experiencing long queues, but we are working as fast as we can in order to help everyone
Kind regards, Rebecka

@Bridie51960784 Hi! 

Yes it's possible that we have restricted the sales for that period but i sadly can't see if we will offer flights for that period again.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@yamu06 Hi!

I´m are really sorry about the change of the flight, I recommend you to take contact with my colleges over the phone and they will help you look for alternatives about the booking, you can find the local number by this link https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

kind regards, Kevin

@karlosjod Hello, I'm sorry to hear that she was denied boarding due to missing PCR test. For more information about the entry rules for your destination please go to https://t.co/oj06rsDGPg or contact the local authorities directly.

With best regards,
Anton.

@ConsultantMud Hi! I'm terribly sorry about what happened to your case. To report this please bring your baggage to the airport and show it to Baggage Service who will help you make the report. More information can be found at https://t.co/KQdOdrH9TM

Best regards,
Anton.

@eirikwang Hi! From September this year and onward we will have direct flights OSL to KBP every Tuesday and Saturday.

Best regards,
Anton.

@bennokress Hi Benno
Face masks that are allowed on board include single-use masks of FFP2, KN95, N95 standards or surgical masks such as IIR or similar. 
Kind regards /Anna

@Scc40648262 Hello
You can contact us by Facebook messenger , live chat or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards /Anna

@DrCAClarke Hi Caroline
Contact us on live chat, Facebook messenger or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj with your references and we can help you further.
Kind regards /Anna

@megan_cresswell Hi Megan
We can not promise in advance you need to check with the staff at the airport if it is ok.
Kind regards /Anna

@DPassner Hi Dan
If the voucher has expired we can not extend it. If you received it for a cancelled flight from us it is refundable. otherwise not. Contact us on FB messenger or live chat and we can see what type of voucher you have. https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards /Anna

@esjorgen Hej Espen
Kontakta oss på Face book messenger, live chat eller telefon https://t.co/cIkJt9kPnF så skall vi se vad som skett med din refusjon.
Hälsningar/Anna

@CallIrelands Hello
Please contact us on Face book messenger , live chat or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj with your booking reference so we can help you further. We can not support this by Twitter.
Kind regards /Anna

@mrsRganics Hi! I'm sorry to hear that you are still waiting for your voucher. Please contact us via live-chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj with your booking details so we can help you take a look at the status of your voucher issuance.

Best regards,
Anton.

@mr_iiot Hello, the latest information about our lounges during the pandemic can be found at https://t.co/gml5ZaEizi under "Changes to our service".

Best regards,
Anton.

@rob_w_r Hello, if the booking was made through a travel agency we are unfortunately not able to assist with rebooking or cancellation etc matters from here. Only the travel agent can assist you with this.

Best regards,
Anton.

@NotMaryAnthony Hi. We apologize for the longer than usual wait times on the phone right now. All I can recommend for now is that you try to book the ticket again later or contact us by phone for help.

Best regards,
Anton.

@Damage_13 Hello. You can find information about the entry restrictions for your destination and transit airports at https://t.co/oj06rsDGPg - If you need more information then this we recommend that you contact the local authorities directly.

Best regards,
Anton.

@NotMaryAnthony Hello! I'm sorry to hear you are experiencing problems with our website. Please try clearing cache/cookies in your web browser to see if that helps. If the problem persists you can call our phone support for help with booking or rebooking https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

//
Anton.

@AlltidAmanda Hi. I recommend that you try to clear cache/cookies in your web browser to see if that helps. If the problem persists you can call our phone support for help with booking. Phone numbers can be located at https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.
